    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >QQ群：862919343</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >※游戏可以自定义按键，包括手柄和键鼠，手柄有震动。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >※如果手柄没反应请按照以下设置：右键点击游戏名字→属性→控制器→使用默认设置或禁用steam输入。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >【本游戏目前有两关，第三关会在2026年初更新，原价会随着内容增加而提高。】</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《斩夜》是一款由我个人用unity开发和个人发行的鬼泣Like高速纯动作游戏。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >玩家可以在游戏中体验到即时快速切换武器进行空中或地面自由连击的爽快战斗。本游戏提供三种难度选择，因为目标是提供爽快自由的战斗体验所以高难度并不是游戏核心，本游戏适合喜欢不拖沓尽情战斗的战斗狂玩家。游戏允许自定义按键</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >【目前武器种类】</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >近程：武士刀（白夜），格斗（雷装），镰刀（苍断）</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >远程：左轮手枪（暗月）</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >【目前总技能数】</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >约33，包含有空战所需的JC（跳跃取消，空中踩踏敌人），二段跳、瞬移和空中闪避等。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >【特色系统】</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >伤害率评价系统：使用不同技能或武器连击则可以提高评价并增加伤害率，伤害率最高1.5倍。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >魔法盾：类似瞬间防御，但不能提前使用，仅可以在快要被击中时使用，成功时会令周围所有敌人动作变慢。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >完美闪避：一般的回避不会触发完美闪避，仅在快要被击中时回避才会触发，成功时会令周围所有敌人动作变慢。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >【目前游戏流程】</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >关卡数：2（最终会有5关）</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >游玩时间：约45分钟以上</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >杂兵种类：5</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >本游戏仍在更新中。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >魔法盾和完美回避可以令到敌人动作变慢，抓住这个机会对敌人进行反击吧！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3291030/extras/cf7da4c4118abef00c3c7f39c2dd7d16.poster.avif?t=1765108231\" width=450 height=254 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3291030/extras/cf7da4c4118abef00c3c7f39c2dd7d16.webm?t=1765108231\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3291030/extras/cf7da4c4118abef00c3c7f39c2dd7d16.mp4?t=1765108231\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3291030/extras/afd79619de6c0d3ed93763f0c3fb4fe0.poster.avif?t=1765108231\" width=450 height=254 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3291030/extras/afd79619de6c0d3ed93763f0c3fb4fe0.webm?t=1765108231\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3291030/extras/afd79619de6c0d3ed93763f0c3fb4fe0.mp4?t=1765108231\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3291030/extras/e57aeb9566052e20b1af437df113cdcf.poster.avif?t=1765108231\" width=450 height=254 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3291030/extras/e57aeb9566052e20b1af437df113cdcf.webm?t=1765108231\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3291030/extras/e57aeb9566052e20b1af437df113cdcf.mp4?t=1765108231\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >利用踩怪，二段跳，瞬移，空中回避来打出华丽的空中连击，空中攻击可以令到伤害率更容易地增加。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3291030/extras/842ff2567e03a5276fc3305462f8a561.poster.avif?t=1765108231\" width=450 height=254 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3291030/extras/842ff2567e03a5276fc3305462f8a561.webm?t=1765108231\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3291030/extras/842ff2567e03a5276fc3305462f8a561.mp4?t=1765108231\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >消耗能量释放高伤害技能。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3291030/extras/089dd554874fef05448822f4dd68d8fc.poster.avif?t=1765108231\" width=450 height=254 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3291030/extras/089dd554874fef05448822f4dd68d8fc.webm?t=1765108231\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3291030/extras/089dd554874fef05448822f4dd68d8fc.mp4?t=1765108231\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >切换不同武器，打出华丽的连击。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3291030/extras/5846805fb69ad329b4a06f4ff0aecf8b.poster.avif?t=1765108231\" width=450 height=254 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3291030/extras/5846805fb69ad329b4a06f4ff0aecf8b.webm?t=1765108231\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3291030/extras/5846805fb69ad329b4a06f4ff0aecf8b.mp4?t=1765108231\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3291030/extras/2fa4d0eb8a7d35c091b3723397789aa4.poster.avif?t=1765108231\" width=450 height=254 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3291030/extras/2fa4d0eb8a7d35c091b3723397789aa4.webm?t=1765108231\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3291030/extras/2fa4d0eb8a7d35c091b3723397789aa4.mp4?t=1765108231\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
